data.title: UN Secretariat Documentation
data.meta_description: Information about the documentation related to the UN Secretariat and the Secretaries-General.
data.text:
Kofi Annan (Ghana) served as the seventh Secretary-General from 1997-2006.

Appointed: A/RES/51/200, A/51/PV.88 of 17 Dec. 1996

1st inaugural speech: A/51/PV.88

Re-appointed: A/RES/55/277, A/55/PV.105 of 29 June 2001

2nd inaugural speech: A/55/PV.105

Tribute resolution: S/RES/1733 (2006), S/PV.5607 of 22 Dec. 2006

UN press release biography of 2002: [ST/DPI/PRESS/] SG/2031/Rev.6-BIO/3053/Rev.6
